    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Distinctive handbells or gongs, used as an instrument in Indian music and in Buddhist ritual. A ghanta may be paired with a vajra; use the more specific "vajras-ghantas."</Note_Text>
